Java_Reviews


IntelliJ Shortcut:
    Mac:
        reformating the codes:  option + command + L

        main method: main + Enter

        print statements: sout + Enter

        print variable: soutv + Enter


    Windows:
        reformating the codes:  alt + cntrl + L

        main method: main +Enter

        print variable: soutv + Enter

        print statements: sout + Enter



escape Sequences:

    \t: horizontal tab

    \n: new line

    \": double quote

    \\: back slash




